Uses of Package
primary

  • Packages that use primary 
    Package Description
    primary  
  • Classes in primary used by primary 
    Class and Description
    Capture
    Capture class that captures a styrofoam block once the detect object has detected such a block.
    ColorSensor
    Color Sensor that uses the redMode to detect black lines on the ground
    DetectObject
    Goes to an object that has been detected and check whether that object is a wooden block or a styrofoam block.
    DodgeObject
    This class dodges a wooden brick in most case by using the front and side sensors.
    GoToZone
    This thread assumes the robot is holding a block and only has to go to the appropriate zone.
    LCDInfo
    Prints the value reported by the odometer on the EV3's LCD screen.
    Localization
    The localization class localizes the robot in the corresponding corner.
    Navigation 
    Odometer
    Takes value from the tachometer and gives a somewhat precise estimation of the current position.
    OdometerCorrection
    This class uses the color sensor aiming to the ground to determine black lines on the competition board.
    SearchAndMove
    Algorithm to move the robot when it did not detect any blocks.
    USSensor
    This class uses the sensor sensor or the side sensor , filters its result and return its values.
